title: Pharga pallens
data: Pharga pallens is a species of moth in the family Erebidae.[1][2] It was first described by William Barnes and James Halliday McDunnough in 1911 and it is found in North America.[1] The MONA or Hodges number for Pharga pallens is 8516.[3] This article on a moth of the family Erebidae is a stub.
